  "answer": "def copyRandomList(head):\n    if not head: return None\n    m = {None: None}\n    cur = head\n    while cur: m[cur] = Node(cur.val); cur = cur.next\n    cur = head\n    while cur:\n        m[cur].next = m[cur.next]\n        m[cur].random = m[cur.random]\n        cur = cur.next\n    return m[head]",
